  <body>

    <!--Navbar-->
    <div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-inner">
        <div class="container">
          <a href="#action" class="brand">Join the Pilot Test</a>
          <div class="pull-right">
            <a href="mailto:evelyn@hirable.org?Subject=Hello%20There!" class="brand">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>
    </div>

    <!--Top Container-->

    <div class="row-fluid top-container text-center">
      <% if flash[:success] %>
      <h4 id="success" class="text-success"><%= flash[:success] %></h4>
      <br>
      <% end %>

      <div class="container">
          <div class="span7">
            <img src="../assets/original.png">
          </div>
            <!--Right Message Box with Call to Action-->
            <div class="span5 text-center" style="">
              <h2 class="text-center">High Quality Referrals</h2>
              <h3 class="text-center">with Recursive Rewards</h3><br>
              <div class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-large btn-warning" href="#action">Join the Pilot Test</a></div><br><br>
              <p class="lead" style="text-align: justify;">No matter where you are in the referral chain, be rewarded for insights on great candidates or employers. Keep any rewards you earn while helping us pilot test the concept. Our pilot will include referral bonuses ranging up to $15,000. </p>
            </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!--Middle Panels-->
    <div class="container marketing">

      <!-- Three columns of text below the main container -->

      <a name="action"></a>
      <div class="row-fluid action">
        <div class="span4">
          <h2><img src="../assets/Originator.png"><b>Originator</b></h2>
          <div class="lead">
            <p><b>Who:</b> You are a hiring manager or passionate employee. Your company has a referral bonus policy. 
            <p><b>Why:</b> You are searching for the best hire and will share rewards with those who help.</p>
            <p><b>How:</b> List search criteria &rarr; Offer a reward &rarr; Send out.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mobile-version">
            <%= render "originator" %>
          </div>
        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
        <div class="span4">
          <h2><img src="../assets/Referrer.png"><b>Referrer</b></h2>
          <div class="lead">
            <p><b>Who:</b> You are a natural connector. You know lots of people. You take pride in tracking what people need. </p>
            <p><b>Why:</b> Get rewarded for doing what you already do best. Make recruiting warmer for all.</p>
            <p><b>How:</b> Receive postings &rarr; Give high quality insights &rarr; Refer.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mobile-version">
            <%= render "referrer" %>           
          </div>
        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
        <div class="span4">
          <h2><img src="../assets/Candidate.png"><b>Candidate</b></h2>
          <div class="lead">
            <p><b>Who:</b> You are fantastic talent. You're an opportunity for the right team. You want to create your own role and impact. </p>
            <p><b>Why:</b> You deserve high quality referrals. You want exposure to greater volume of teams.</p>
            <p><b>How:</b> List search criteria &rarr; Receive referrals &rarr; Apply.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mobile-version">
            <%= render "candidate" %>
          </div>            
        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
      </div><!-- /.row -->

      <div class="row-fluid desktop-version">
        <div class="span4">
          <%= render "originator" %>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
            <%= render "referrer" %>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">    
            <%= render "candidate" %>
          </div>
        </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <!--Slider Widget-->
      <div class="featurette">
        <div class="featurette-block featurette-image pull-right">
          <div class="flex-video">
            <iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/F6qzfLI2Qsc?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2>Recursive Rewards <span class="muted featurette-sub-heading"><br>Simply Explained</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Your peers may not know the right person for the job, but their contacts can open up promising talent communities. Motivate those outside your immediate circle of peers by offering them an equal part of the referral bonus. We'll keep track of the sequential referrals, and ensure they are trustworthy and high quality. When a candidate is hired, we reward everyone who was part of the solution. </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <!--MIT Media Lab-->
      <div class="featurette">
        <div class="featurette-block featurette-image pull-left">
          <img src="../assets/Map-Animation.gif">
        </div><div class="featurette-block">
          <h2>MIT Media Lab <span class="muted featurette-sub-heading"><br>Experiment Applied</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">In a nationwide sourcing challenge hosted by DARPA, the MIT Media Lab was the only team to use recursive rewards. It paid off: They recruited nearly 5000 participants in under 9 hours, making them three times more successful than any other team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br><br>
        
      <div class="text-center">
          <a class="btn btn-large btn-warning" href="#action">Join the Pilot Test</a><br>
      </div>

      <br>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <footer>
        <p class="pull-right"><a href="#">Back to top</a></p>
        <p>&copy; 2013 Hirable.org</p>
      </footer>
    </div>

